column16: Ian Kinsler singles on a ground ball to left fielder Brandon Guyer.   James McCann scores.    Jose Iglesias to 3rd.    Ian Kinsler to 2nd on the throw.
Jose Iglesias singles on a ground ball to left fielder Brandon Guyer.   James McCann to 2nd.
Erick Aybar called out on strikes and Justin Upton caught stealing 2nd, catcher Adam Moore to shortstop Erik Gonzalez.
J.  D.   Martinez strikes out swinging.
Justin Morneau grounds into a force out, shortstop Francisco Lindor to second baseman Jason Kipnis.   Jose Abreu out at 2nd.
Jose Abreu singles on a ground ball to left fielder Coco Crisp.   Melky Cabrera to 2nd.
Melky Cabrera singles on a ground ball to left fielder Coco Crisp.   Leury Garcia scores.
Leury Garcia singles on a ground ball to center fielder Rajai Davis.
Carlos Sanchez flies out to left fielder Coco Crisp in foul territory.
Perci Garner intentionally walks Miguel Cabrera.
Cameron Maybin pops out to second baseman Jason Kipnis.
Ian Kinsler grounds out, shortstop Francisco Lindor to first baseman Mike Napoli.   Jose Iglesias to 3rd.
Todd Frazier singles on a sharp line drive to right fielder Lonnie Chisenhall.   Todd Frazier to 2nd.  Jose Abreu advances to 3rd, on a fielding error by right fielder Lonnie Chisenhall.
White Sox challenged (tag-up play), call on the field was overturned: Justin Morneau lines out to shortstop Francisco Lindor.
Melky Cabrera grounds out to first baseman Mike Napoli.
Max Kepler singles on a line drive to center fielder Rajai Davis.   Jorge Polanco to 2nd.
Jorge Polanco singles on a line drive to left fielder Coco Crisp.
Joe Mauer grounds out, second baseman Jason Kipnis to first baseman Carlos Santana.
Brian Dozier strikes out on a foul tip.
James Beresford grounds out, pitcher Perci Garner to first baseman Carlos Santana.
Alex Bregman triples (3) on a sharp line drive to center fielder Tyler Naquin.   George Springer scores.
Jose Altuve grounds into a double play, shortstop Francisco Lindor to second baseman Jason Kipnis to first baseman Mike Napoli.   Alex Bregman out at 2nd.
Alex Bregman reaches on a fielding error by second baseman Jason Kipnis.
George Springer strikes out on a foul tip.
Jake Marisnick singles on a line drive to center fielder Tyler Naquin.
Teoscar Hernandez grounds out, third baseman Jose Ramirez to first baseman Mike Napoli.
Colby Rasmus grounds out to first baseman Mike Napoli.
Evan Gattis flies out to right fielder Lonnie Chisenhall.
Yulieski Gurriel grounds into a force out, pitcher Perci Garner to shortstop Francisco Lindor.   Carlos Correa out at 2nd.    Yulieski Gurriel to 1st.
Eduardo Escobar grounds out softly to first baseman Mike Napoli.   Eddie Rosario to 3rd.    Jorge Polanco to 2nd.
Jorge Polanco singles on a soft line drive to center fielder Rajai Davis.   Eddie Rosario to 2nd.
Eddie Rosario singles on a line drive to right fielder Lonnie Chisenhall.
